parameters: \n<Zane> I've been Trying to tell you...
\n<Zane> It was one disaster after another.
And now, the crops are dead. But I know it
wasn't you, It was the water.
\n<Zane> I've managed to convince a few,
but the rest remain firm. Many are trying
to travel to the mainland now.
\n<Zane> Are you sure you won't come with us?
\n<Zaphilia> And I've kept telling you Zane,
\n<Zane> You may not be able to get onto
the airship, but I know someone
who may be able to help.
village for you ever since you left.
\n<Zaphilia> Soon... I can go to Zendir...
